    "body": "my argument *for* curly braces is that it not just improves visual readability, but also helps alot in jumping forth and back in your editor via shortcuts. I personally do that a lot in VIM to jump based on braces.\r\n\r\nNot having such a syntactic sugar would just make moving around less convenient.",
